    "notes": "Low in elliptic@6.6.1 via vite-plugin-node-polyfills > node-stdlib-browser > crypto-browserify (dev dep). Risky crypto implementation. All versions affected, no fix available. crypto-browserify is not imported by app code; only bundled if a dep references it."
