    "notes": "Moderate in brace-expansion@5.0.5 bundled inside npm CLI via @semantic-release/npm > npm > minimatch (dev/release tooling). DoS via crafted ranges, not exploitable on trusted CI input. Fix requires upstream npm release bundling brace-expansion>=5.0.6."
